# The repository-level .gitignore treats all JSON/CSV/JSONL as private data by
# default. Everything in this benchmark is synthetic and Claude-authored (no
# client or survey data), so it is explicitly re-included for reproducibility.
!*.json
!*.jsonl
!*.csv

# Raw run outputs stay out of git (large); analysis summaries and hashes are
# committed under analysis/ instead.
results/
